        "gate": "MultiDriverDispatcher",
        "outcome": "dispatched"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "REQ-5",
      "text": "If no driver accepts within the dispatch window, the platform automatically reassigns by recycling the ride request for a new dispatch attempt.",
